track_notes: Nice hike on the Appalachian Trail to a great SOTA summit.

4.5 mile hike with 1800 feet EG.  Large parking area at Winding Stair Gap on Hwy 64 (35.121724, -83.544450).  Head north on the AT for 4.25 miles and take a left to climb the final 200 feet of EG to the open grassy bald.
track_title: W4C/WM-024 - Siler Bald via Winding Stairs Gap
